  "general_provisions": "This bill establishes a charter school base funding study and creates a charter school educational service agency.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>requires a study of charter school administrative costs and funding options;<hr><ltbullet>establishes a charter school base funding study group with specific membership;<hr><ltbullet>requires charter school governing board members to take an oath of office;<hr><ltbullet>clarifies that charter schools are public schools;<hr><ltbullet>replaces the Charter School Revolving Account with the Charter School Revolving Fund; <hr><ltbullet>requires the study group to examine charter school administrative costs and funding options;<hr><ltbullet>directs the State Board of Education to report to the Legislature by December 1, 2026; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical changes.",
